outputs.output_descr: The UNREDD programme strengthens' Tanzania's readiness for REDD as a component of the Government's evolving REDD strategy.  It is integrated with other REDD activities in the country. Planned activities cover 24 months, laying the groundwork for activities in later years.  the initiative is an integral part of the ONE UN Programme and the Joint Programme on Environment.

project_descr: Reducing Emissions from Deforestation and Forest Degradation
